      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R2) is a commercially validated code with documented SQA processes including version control, regression testing, and release validation. A solver verification report was reviewed confirming compliance with ISO 9001 quality management and ASME V&V 10 SQA requirements. Internal SQA log for the project-specific UDF implementing the power-law hemolysis model was reviewed; unit tests confirmed correct implementation of the Giersiepen-Wurzinger coefficients.",
