      "rationale": "Code verification performed using the method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver. Observed order of accuracy (p=1.93) is consistent with the nominal second-order spatial discretization scheme. Benchmark comparisons against the FDA critical path CFD benchmark (lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step) showed velocity profile agreement within 2% of published reference data.",
