      "rationale": "GCI study on three systematically refined meshes yields GCI_fine=3.1% on NIH at the worst-case operating point, below the 5% acceptance threshold. Richardson extrapolation performed and asymptotic convergence confirmed. The fine mesh (19.2M cells) with y+=1 wall treatment is used for all production runs. Discretization error is quantified and bounded as part of the total uncertainty budget.",
