      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions for the validation dataset are documented in the FDA hemolysis testing protocol. Flow rates (2–6 L/min), rotational speeds (1500–3500 RPM), fluid properties (Newtonian blood analog, viscosity 3.5 cP), and temperature (37±0.5 °C) are all specified with measurement uncertainties. Boundary conditions applied in the CFD model are directly traceable to the experimental test report. Deviations between experimental and simulated conditions are documented and bounded.",
