      "rationale": "CFD predictions of NIH and pump head are compared against experimental measurements using quantitative metrics: mean absolute error, relative error, and validation uncertainty interval. All five operating points fall within the validation uncertainty band. Comparison plots and tabulated residuals are documented in the validation report. The relative hemolysis index (RH = NIH_device/NIH_predicate) is computed from validated NIH predictions.",
