      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used in the COU, at operating conditions spanning the full COU operating envelope (2–6 L/min, 1500–3500 RPM). Fluid properties match the COU blood analog specification. The validation activities directly support the COU claim of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. No significant extrapolation beyond the validation domain is required for the COU predictions.",
