      "rationale": "All model inputs (geometry, fluid properties, boundary conditions, hemolysis model coefficients) are documented with sources and uncertainties. Geometry is derived from the FDA generic pump CAD file with dimensional tolerances specified. Fluid properties are taken from published blood analog characterization data. Hemolysis model coefficients are taken from Giersiepen et al. (1990) with reported 95% confidence intervals. Input uncertainty propagation is included in the UQ assessment.",
